elements.name: As a user I create a post using plus button on home page

steps.name: I set scenario "Post_creation_plus_button" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-secondary-action.gh-nav-new-post.ember-view"
I enter "$name_1" into input field having css selector ".gh-editor-title"
I enter "$name_2" into input field having css selector ".koenig-editor__editor"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/posts/']"
